        <h1>Product Management in Movelys</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            Product management is a fundamental pillar of any business management solution, and Movelys meets this requirement with power, precision, and flexibility. This module allows users to centralize all information related to products from their initial registration to their complete lifecycle, including stock management, pricing, categories, locations, and much more.
        </p>
        <p>
            With an intuitive interface and advanced features, the "Products" module of Movelys enables users to record, classify, and track items with great rigor. It supports multi-site management, tracking of purchase and sale prices, real-time stock, SKUs, categories, brands, units of measure, taxes, and specific information for each product.
        </p>
        <p>
            This system integrates seamlessly with other Movelys modules such as purchases, sales, stock transfers, and reports. Thus, each product becomes a traceable and controlled entity, facilitating smooth commercial management, better visibility on margins, and more effective strategic decision-making.
        </p>
    </section>

